      • DEFAULT_NODE_WEIGHT

        public static final java.lang.Double DEFAULT_NODE_WEIGHT
        The default node weight value. Note: There does not exist a real default value in GraphStream for this (the default here is when there is no 'layout.weight' attribute stored on the graph) so this default value is defined as Double.NaN.

      • DEFAULT_EDGE_WEIGHT

        public static final java.lang.Double DEFAULT_EDGE_WEIGHT
        The default edge weight value. Note: There does not exist a real default value in GraphStream for this (the default here is when there is no 'layout.weight' attribute stored on the graph) so this default value is defined as Double.NaN.
